         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577"><!-- p2l3-r12 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Hd1e108">Rubrica 12</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De conseruandis et retinendis amicis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
      ¶ De conseruandis et retinendis amicis. Rubrica 12.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e115">SAlomon in prouerb. c. 7.</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e125">Amicum tuum et
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>patris tui ne dimiseris.</quote> 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e131">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e129">Isocrates in exhortationibus. c. i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e135">Decet natos sicut substantie fic etiam pater
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>ne dilectionis esse heredes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e148">¶ </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e152"> ¶
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e149">Aristoteles rethoricorum libro i. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e154">Se
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>parari ab amicis et consuetis miserabile: confu <!--'u' flipped-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>sio: debilitas: orbatio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e162">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e165">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. ca. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e166">Ne dere
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>linquas amicum antiquum: nouus enim non erit
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>similis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e174"> /
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e177">22 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e176">Qui conuiciatur amico: dis
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>soluit amicitiam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>¶<ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e185">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum: lib. 7. c. 5.</ref> Ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>cus animo possidendus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e195">Martialis cocus li. vndique suscepto. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e190">Prudenti probe consilio retinendus amicus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>Quem sero acquiris: sed cito perdis eum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>Frangis amicitiam: dum tarde ledis amicum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>Insidians socio: frangis amicitiam.<!--109.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-d1e207">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Rd1e216">Auctor li. qui dicitur facetus. c. 7.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31577-Qd1e211">Queritur euentu socius: tamen arte tenetur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>Res leuis est querere: sed retinere labor.</quote>
            </p>
